"Presumptious sort, aren't you?  Empath, Terrorize!"  The leopard is 
replaced by the dangerous femme-bot.  "Stay back, or you'll pay for 
it."  Reaching out with her mind, she checks the intentions of the 
natives.  Not hostile, but prepared nonetheless.
